main event: A bright light was seen hovering and then rapidly moving away in Cupar, Scotland on October 24, 1963.
interesting points: The object was observed by two people, the witness and his son's neighbor.
The object made a sound like an electrical generator.
The object was observed through binoculars.
The Air Force was unable to identify the object due to lack of on-site investigation.
witnesses: the witness and his son's neighbor
